Uses of Package
gui.controller

Packages that use gui.controller
Package Description
gui.controller
This package contains the controller classes like SceneController and MovingObjectController.
gui.view
This package contains the classes that implement the stage and the different scenes and panes.
simulator
This package contains the classes to start and store the main information of the game.
  • Classes in gui.controller used by gui.controller
    Class Description
    GameController
    This class implements a timer that enables the player to move around, counts the days and makes the fields grow with timer.
    MovingObjectController
    This class implements some methods to move around and to process the fields.
    MovingObjectFunctionalityController
    This class implements all the actions that are possible when moving around e. g. selecting a vehicle, exiting and entering or unload grain to the silo or sell it at the court trade.
  • Classes in gui.controller used by gui.view
    Class Description
    GameController
    This class implements a timer that enables the player to move around, counts the days and makes the fields grow with timer.
    SceneController
    This class implements the methods, that are responsible for the change of the scene.
  • Classes in gui.controller used by simulator
    Class Description
    GameController
    This class implements a timer that enables the player to move around, counts the days and makes the fields grow with timer.
